<title>SWITZERLAND: CS says sees 35 pct H1 oper profit rise.</title>
<headline>CS says sees 35 pct H1 oper profit rise.</headline>
<dateline>ZURICH 1997-05-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Credit Suisse Group said it had a very good start to 1997 in the first quarter and it expected a clearly better operating result for the first half of 1997 with an operating profit increase of some 35 percent.</p>
<p>A Credit Suisse spokesman said the group's chairman Rainer Gut made the profit outlook statement at the company's annual shareholders meeting.</p>
<p>-- Zurich Editorial +41 1 631 7340</p>
